<p> 
<h3>What is the purpose of this site?</h3> 
Cooking Wheels was created by <a href="http://johncblandii.com">John C. Bland II</a> to serve as a live, relevant open-source application. The purpose of this site is to help <a href="http://cfwheels.org"></a>ColdFusion Wheels</a> developers solve common problems. The site is organized into a set of tags and recipes. Each recipe has a problem, solution, and solution details. The hope is that the reader will come to the site with a problem - find a matching recipe - and be able to leave with a good meal.
</p> 
 
