<h3>What was the inspiration behind the site?</h3>
<p><a href="http://coldfusioncookbook.com">ColdFusionCookbook.com</a> was great inspiration. Heck, even this FAQ is a tweaked version of their FAQ. Cookbooks simply help and <a href="http://coldfusionjedi.com">Ray Camden</a> provided a great model to follow. This site isn't a clone but it is definitely work of collective inspiration.</p>
